OK, Now that I got it all straightened out.

::KitKat::
She looked up at Bloodystrike. "Well, here's a quick update.  
Megatron has managed to clone his warriors.  The Lavacons and 
Starscream are engaging Megatron's forces.  I was going to try to 
talk to Megatron, but Starscream found out it was an ambush and 
started fighting.  We are now heading to the old Pred cave base to 
fight Megatron and his new group." She said as she ran. She really 
was feeling the pain in her side and the pain screamed at her.  She 
had to ignore it for now and worry about the up coming battle.  Her 
mind ran with ideas, but nothing felt right.  She would have to wait 
untill she got there to see the situation her self.
